1) this was uploaded on my birthday which made my quarantine birthday THAT much better on top of my virtual party
2) he gave a shoutout to healthcare workers and that means so much 💕 both of my parents work in the hospital and have continued to work through this pandemic. I’m proud of them but it’s so nice to hear someone like John Krasinski to acknowledge them. It’s scary since my dad had to get tested after one of his close colleagues got tested positive, but the good news is my dad is clear from it.

This is going to be one of the things to keep us going. Thanks John, keep up the amazing work!
